title: Tuesday Afternoon Headlines: Governor signs dozens of bills into law; Speed cameras on deck for JFX; Photos of winners of squirrel contest; and morecontest
body: – The Sun – WBAL News – WBAL-TV – Maryland Matters – The Washington Post – WMAR-TV Explore Baltimore Fishbowl Hot House: Historic mansion on three acres in the heart of Guilford Nearly 1.4 million Marylanders are fully vaccinated against COVID-19 A Bridge to Somewhere: 9 1/2 Hours on Kent Island This TV Series About Maryland Wasn't Filmed in Maryland A Peek Inside John Waters's Baltimore Home Study: Baltimore has seen one of the highest rates of gentrification in the U.S.
